Green: 0.7154;

Blue: 0.0721.

The instance uses R-Y algorithm to convert color image
            to grayscale. The conversion coefficients are:
            

Red: 0.5;

Green: 0.419;

Blue: 0.081.

The instance uses Y algorithm to convert color image
            to grayscale. The conversion coefficients are:
            

